messages.messageBody:
Hi all

Hope you don't mind me joining this group. I live in New Zealand and signed up yesterday. I have been lurking today (hope you don't mind).

My name is Jacqui and my husbands name is Jason we have 1 son Liam who is 4. In NZ children start school at 5. We are going to unschool Liam as I see it as the best thing. Totally againist the grain here, which is why I find this email list rather good.

We have an unschoolers list in NZ but it is very quiet.

I have learn't alot already today, which is great. I have also read alot of books on unschooling which I have really enjoyed.

Thanks for the insight
Jacqui
